## ğŸ“¦ **What are S3 Storage Classes?**

### âœ… Definition

Amazon S3 Storage Classes alag-alag **data access patterns** ke liye design ki gayi storage options hoti hain.

ğŸ‘‰ Matlab:

* Data **kitni baar access hota hai**
* Data **kitne time ke liye store karna hai**
* **Cost vs access speed**

In sab ke basis par storage class choose ki jaati hai.

---

## ğŸ§  **Basic Rule (Easy to Remember)**

* **Zyada access â†’ zyada cost**
* **Kam access â†’ kam cost**
* **Fast access â†’ mehnga**
* **Slow access â†’ sasta**

---

## ğŸŸ¢ **1. S3 Standard**

### âœ… Definition

S3 Standard ek **general-purpose storage class** hai jo **frequently accessed data** ke liye use hoti hai.

---

### ğŸ” Key Features

* Millisecond access
* High availability & durability
* No minimum storage duration

---

### ğŸ§  Real-Life Example

* Website images
* Videos
* Mobile app data

---

### ğŸ¯ Use Case

* Data jo **daily ya frequently access** hota hai

---

## ğŸ”µ **2. S3 Intelligent-Tiering**

### âœ… Definition

S3 Intelligent-Tiering automatically data ko **different access tiers** me move karta hai based on usage.

ğŸ‘‰ Tumhe manually decide karne ki zarurat nahi.

---

### ğŸ” How it Works

* Frequently accessed â†’ Frequent tier
* 30 days no access â†’ Infrequent tier
* 90 days no access â†’ Archive tier
* 180 days no access â†’ Deep Archive tier

---

### ğŸ§  Real-Life Example

* YouTube videos (kab viral ho jaaye pata nahi)
* Logs jinka access pattern unknown ho

---

### ğŸ¯ Use Case

* Jab data ka **future access pattern unknown** ho

---

## ğŸŸ¡ **3. S3 Standard-Infrequent Access (S3 Standard-IA)**

### âœ… Definition

Long-lived data jo **kam access hota hai**, lekin jab chahiye to **fast access** chahiye.

---

### ğŸ” Key Features

* Lower storage cost than Standard
* Millisecond access
* Retrieval cost lagta hai

---

### ğŸ§  Real-Life Example

* Backup files
* Disaster recovery data

---

## ğŸŸ  **4. S3 One Zone-Infrequent Access (S3 One Zone-IA)**

### âœ… Definition

S3 Standard-IA jaisa hi hai, bas data **sirf ek Availability Zone** me store hota hai.

---

### ğŸ” Key Features

* Cost aur kam
* Single AZ (less durable)

---

### ğŸ§  Real-Life Example

* Re-creatable data
* Temporary backups

---

## â„ï¸ **5. S3 Glacier Instant Retrieval**

### âœ… Definition

Archive data ke liye jise **kabhi-kabhi turant access** chahiye.

---

### ğŸ” Key Features

* Low storage cost
* Millisecond retrieval

---

### ğŸ§  Use Case

* Medical records
* Compliance data

---

## â„ï¸ **6. S3 Glacier Flexible Retrieval (Earlier: Glacier)**

### âœ… Definition

Long-term archive data jise **rarely access** kiya jata hai.

---

### ğŸ” Key Features

* Retrieval time: minutes to hours
* Storage cost low

---

### ğŸ§  Use Case

* Audit logs
* Old backups

---

## ğŸ§Š **7. S3 Glacier Deep Archive**

### âœ… Definition

Sabse **sasta storage class**, long-term data ke liye jise **bahut kam access** kiya jata hai.

---

### ğŸ” Key Features

* Retrieval time: hours
* Lowest cost

---

### ğŸ§  Real-Life Example

* 7â€“10 saal purane records
* Legal archives

---

## ğŸ“Š **Storage Classes Comparison (Easy Table)**

| Storage Class       | Access     | Cost      | Use Case       |
| ------------------- | ---------- | --------- | -------------- |
| S3 Standard         | Frequent   | High      | Active data    |
| Intelligent-Tiering | Unknown    | Optimized | Dynamic data   |
| Standard-IA         | Infrequent | Lower     | Backups        |
| One Zone-IA         | Infrequent | Cheaper   | Re-creatable   |
| Glacier Instant     | Rare       | Low       | Archive + fast |
| Glacier Flexible    | Very Rare  | Lower     | Long-term      |
| Deep Archive        | Very Rare  | Lowest    | Cold archive   |

