## ğŸ§  **Hotel Example (Class Explanation Style)**

* **City Center Hotel** â†’ S3 Standard (mehnga, fast)
* **Outskirts Hotel** â†’ Standard-IA
* **Village Hotel** â†’ Glacier
* **Store Room Godown** â†’ Deep Archive

ğŸ‘‰ Stay = Storage cost
ğŸ‘‰ Taxi = Access cost

